ҫҺиӮЎиӘҚзңҹиЁҺи«–еҚҖ boardпјҢж…ўж…ўжҗ¬йҮҺдёҠеҺ»гҖӮ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F513A9wIT&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ae2a52d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT</a><br />\n<br />\nй–Ӣе·ҰеҖӢзҫҺиӮЎиӘҚзңҹиЁҺи«–еҚҖпјҲе…Ёж°‘з·ЁијҜз•ҷиЁҖеҚҖпјүпјҢе·ҙжү“еҸҜд»ҘеҠ йҮҺдёҠеҺ»пјҢе‘Ёжң«жңүз©әжңғж•ҙзҗҶ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=f2d82b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3</a><br />\n<br />\nиЁҳеҫ—з”ЁеҒҮеҗҚ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://temp-mail.org/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftemp-mail.org%2Fen%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=0f07c458\" target=\"_blank\">https://temp-mail.org/en/</a><br />\n<br />\nиЁҳеҫ—иҰҒеҠ е·ҰдёӢйқўжўқlink memberе…ҲеҸҜд»Ҙз•ҷиЁҖ<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/invite/b/1SNId2E3/b3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%88%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Finvite%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3%2Fb3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2582%25A1%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%258D%2580%25EF%25BC%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25EF%25BC%2589&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=f5c34b5a